snippet.title: BeamNG.drive - Showreel Trailer
snippet.description:
A dynamic soft-body physics vehicle simulator capable of doing just about anything.

Available now in Early Access:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/284160/BeamNGdrive/
https://www.humblebundle.com/store/beamngdrive

Official website: https://www.beamng.com/game/

Featured mods:
- Mono Milano Spider (by dragoso): https://www.beamng.com/resources/20995/
- Toy Building Block Car (by Agent_Y): https://www.beamng.com/resources/26315/
- Eastern Oregon, USA (by DaddelZeit): https://www.beamng.com/resources/27270/
- Hirochi Talent (by Docroswagge): https://www.beamng.com/resources/31210/
- Ibishu Claria (by LJ74): https://www.beamng.com/resources/23101/
- Seragi Shiba (by Secrane): https://www.beamng.com/resources/22444/
- Serpent Brawler (by Secrane): https://www.beamng.com/resources/23005/

Follow us for more:
Discord: https://www.discord.gg/beamng
Twitter: https://twitter.com/beamng
Facebook: http://facebook.com/BeamNGPhysics
Instagram: https://instagram.com/beamng.official

Music: https://soundcloud.com/gabester/bliont
